{"word":"G4837 - συμπαρακαλέω - symparakaléō - soom-par-ak-al-eh'-o - Comfort together","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπαρακαλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>symparakaléō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>soom-par-ak-al-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Comfort together"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கூட ஆறுதலடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to call upon or invite or exhort at the same time or together"},{"paragraph":"2. to strengthen (comfort) with others"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G3870 - παρακαλέω - parakaléō - par-ak-al-eh'-o/3870\">G3870</a>; to <i>console jointly:</i> - comfort together."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}